dct_title_s: Prospectus Sanctæ olim et celeberrimæ urbis Hierosolymæ
dct_alternative_sm: Prospectus Sanctae olim et celeberrimae urbis Hierosolymae
Prospekt der vormals Heiligen und Welt Berühmten Stadt Jerusalem
dct_description_sm: Coordinates approximate and based on Greenwich meridian.
Shows topography, drainage, places of historical interest.
Includes 2 indexes: Erklaerung der Zahlen -- [Sites of interest].
Appears in Seutter's Grosser Atlas. Augsburg, 1734.
